ump must\nnot modify his past shocking attitude but to appeal to a different spectrum of\nfrozen prejudices, which are common to both Democrats and Republicans.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2016 16:51:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-24"}
