ation with an incident fluence above 10 mJ/cm2 in bulk\nbismuth brings the lattice structure directly into the high-symmetry\nconfiguration for tens of picoseconds, after which carrier relaxation and\ndiffusion restore the equilibrium lattice configuration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2016 20:57:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Sep 2017 08:20:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 24 Nov 2017 19:57:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-03"}
