ple ones) or to a baseline representation selection algorithm\nwhere the encoding parameters are decided a priori for all the views.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Sep 2016 10:01:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-15"}
