ial nanowire, without the need for impurity doping nor requiring the\nformation of a heterojunction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Sep 2016 14:22:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Sep 2016 11:21:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-02"}
